OL,3,CSouthport killer may have targeted
OL,4,Cchildren because of 'society value'
OL,6,FThe brother of the Southport killer
OL,7,Ftold the public inquiry into his
OL,8,Fattack he believes his sibling
OL,9,Ftargeted children because it would
OL,10,F"hurt societies particularly badly".
OL,12,FDion gave evidence over videolink to
OL,13,Fthe Southport Inquiry for a second day
OL,14,Fat Liverpool Town Hall on Wednesday 5
OL,15,FNovember.
OL,17,FThe screen showing him was shielded
OL,18,Ffrom public view.
