OL,3,CSouthport killer may have targeted
OL,4,Cchildren because of 'society value'
OL,6,FThe 21-year-old is two years older
OL,7,Fthan AR, who murdered Elsie Dot
OL,8,FStancombe, seven, Bebe King, six, and
OL,9,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, at a
OL,10,FTaylor Swift-themed dance class on
OL,11,FJuly 29 last year.
OL,13,FThe eldest sibling moved away to
OL,14,Funiversity in 2022 but would return to
OL,15,Fthe family home in Old School Close,
OL,16,FBanks, Lancashire, during holidays.
