OL,3,CSouthport killer may have targeted
OL,4,Cchildren because of 'society value'
OL,6,FDion told the inquiry he was upstairs
OL,7,Fon the morning of 29 July when he saw
OL,8,Fhis brother leave the house wearing a
OL,9,Fface mask.
OL,11,FHe said: "I was going to go into the
OL,12,Fshower on the landing.
OL,14,F"He came upstairs, walked into his
OL,15,Froom, turned round, closed the door
OL,16,Fand then went out of the house."
OL,18,FHe said he did not believe his brother
OL,19,Fhad left the house since March 2022,
OL,20,Fwhen he was arrested on a bus with a
OL,21,Fknife.
