OL,6,FHe told the inquiry: "I got a bit
OL,7,Fnervous initially, I was quite
OL,8,Fsurprised. My mum then got up, I think
OL,9,Fshe might have been in bed.
OL,11,F"The idea that he was going on a walk
OL,12,Fcame about and my parents seemed very
OL,13,Fsure of this.
OL,15,FRichard Boyle, counsel to the inquiry,
OL,16,Fasked: "Your worry was that he wasn't
OL,17,Fgoing on a walk, but would go out to
OL,18,Fcarry an attack?"
OL,20,FDion replied: "Initially, potentially,
OL,21,Fyes."
