OL,3,CSouthport killer may have targeted
OL,4,Cchildren because of 'society value'
OL,6,FHe said he became less worried because
OL,7,Fhis parents appeared to believe his
OL,8,Fbrother had gone for a walk.
OL,10,FHe said shortly after AR left the
OL,11,Fhouse his mother showed him packaging
OL,12,Ffrom a knife, said to have been found
OL,13,Fin the washing machine.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Dion he said there
OL,16,Fwere no discussions about contacting
OL,17,Fthe police at that point.
