OL,6,FIn a statement given to the inquiry,
OL,7,FDion also said: "I was and continue to
OL,8,Fbe devastated and deeply saddened by
OL,9,Fthe immense pain, anguish and grief my
OL,10,Fbrother inflicted on July 29 2024 and
OL,11,FI want to express my deepest
OL,12,Fcondolences to all those involved."
OL,14,FAR's father, Alphonse, is due to give
OL,15,Fevidence later on Wednesday.
